Package: ACERT
Type: Package
Title: Agent-Based Model of Complex Life Cycle Evolution - R Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-01-01
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jesus A.", "Lopez",  role = "aut"),
    person("Robert", "Page",  role = "aut"),
    person("Ashley I.", "Teufel", 
           email = "ateufel@tamusa.edu", 
           role  = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: An R package for analyzing outputs from agent-based models
    of complex life cycle evolution. Includes functions for data wrangling, turtle
    property analysis, population genetics calculations, patch visualization, and
    assessment of replicate run outcomes. Optimized for handling large datasets.
